{"tid":2491762,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"Whizoo Euphemia 尋車cam同目擊者 ［狗狗已去世］","createTime":"2021-04-16T14:06:21.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-16T15:23:04.000Z","uid":234399,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"034fb9724a3dc836e8ed8386ffe3edf94f7238f1","tid":2491762,"uid":234399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T14:06:21.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><strong>以下轉自Euphemia Instagram同Facebook</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n事緣係我今日下午3點50左右，同狗狗(8歲，中型貴婦，大約6kg重）散步經過魚角村對面嘅廢車場。<br />\n本身我聽到一下狗吠聲，都已經想過馬路行返去對面。<br />\n但去到一半，已經見到<strong>有一隻大型嘅唐狗(其實我唔太確定，因為佢個樣都有啲似狼犬)<br />\n我想即刻抱起我隻狗，但都唔夠佢快，佢一下已經咬住咗我隻狗嘅肚。<br />\n我不斷推不斷打佢都唔放口，我一個女仔完全對佢做唔成傷害。</strong><br />\n到之後再有兩隻大狗出現。<br />\n其後我不斷叫救命<br />\n有兩位先生停低幫我<br />\n但過程中我隻狗已經分別被<span class=\"red\">咬到頸、肚、腳</span>。<br />\n終於到佢哋放口，被兩位男士隔開<br />\n我隻狗已經成口鮮血，而且無咩反應。<br />\n其中一位男士好好咁車咗我去動物醫院<br />\n到最後<strong>狗狗因為重傷，我選擇同佢安樂死</strong>。<br />\n我已經報咗警，我希望會搵到車cam片段，同時都想警惕大家呢個位置。<br />\n嗰隻狗真係無啦啦衝出嚟，事前我隻狗完全無吠。<br />\n我好驚會再發生同類意外<br />\n狗又好人也好。<br />\n相信各位主人見到自己嘅狗狗係咁樣流血不止嘅情況下離走，都會頂唔順<br />\n我唔想再發生呢啲事<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmYe2a3jLaJguTyZo7DjZjU2vAZEaXig7gGzwF1m6PiMdx?filename=Mou2EpK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMou2EpK.png&h=c7cbe1b4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmck2uWZL5CC6s4MbwP2NFzSik2JRdXCeSmyMjkvkrvVbU?filename=Gu9J8h4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGu9J8h4.png&h=8bf3df69&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmerujCXM6jks3dpYjUGRF8369M7qNWNY2vRMQcF9uGSPv?filename=Gn5mawr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGn5mawr.png&h=ab1afa8d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7882b2827f3cdb061040c54abad3dda033517cde","tid":2491762,"uid":228955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T14:08:25.000Z","msg":"Up"},{"pid":"bfae4356f9ce7b14d303be51bc54d43fd862d790","tid":2491762,"uid":242444,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T14:15:46.000Z","msg":"好慘<br />\n咩人會放養呢啲唐狗"},{"pid":"e859324c2a07839c23c0d4200ad5c75169ddefc5","tid":2491762,"uid":234399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bfae4356f9ce7b14d303be51bc54d43fd862d790","tid":2491762,"uid":242444,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T14:15:46.000Z","msg":"好慘<br />\n咩人會放養呢啲唐狗"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T14:21:22.000Z","msg":"村屋好多仆街狗主放養！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今次出事個條路都算係假期入大尾篤踩單車必經之地<br />\n下一次出事嘅可能係區外人<br />\n（P牌推唔郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）"},{"pid":"4c160ab4359b4df2b8f162e7d85af52733554763","tid":2491762,"uid":14983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T14:22:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5fa444393dffa62915da743ef4dc674df8a7ddd","tid":2491762,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T14:24:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"82ade577024797c3984947885ddb01911bdf87e0","tid":2491762,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T14:25:46.000Z","msg":"唉 最仆街都係啲人 養狗又唔管理好 結果害死其他狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4900d8ace4fc3cc13fbe253b96994998ddba775","tid":2491762,"uid":301989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T14:50:36.000Z","msg":"推下"},{"pid":"c66f4cd4ce4b4c094f1fe412d885ad98e084c80a","tid":2491762,"uid":230169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T15:12:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5e1db6c0cfa2130236b96b0b28cff0189846364b","tid":2491762,"uid":12557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e859324c2a07839c23c0d4200ad5c75169ddefc5","tid":2491762,"uid":234399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bfae4356f9ce7b14d303be51bc54d43fd8